            "text": "A suspect behind the wheel of a stolen Chevy Camaro crashed into a 2000 GMC Sierra, killing the other driver. The horrific event, which unfolded just before midnight on May 18 in Detroit, perfectly illustrates the vehicle theft crime wave isn’t just merely an inconvenience but a serious threat to public safety.",
